                </div>
                
                <div class="case-study-card" style="opacity: 0.6;">
                    <h3>Legacy System Modernization</h3>
                    <p>Infrastructure migration strategy ensuring business continuity while systematically updating core systems and improving operational efficiency.</p>
                    <p style="font-style: italic; color: #666;">üìù Detailed case study coming soon</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>